<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Sanction Letter - {{applicationNumber}}</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #1a1a2e;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .bank-name {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .bank-tagline {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #64748b;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .doc-meta {
      text-align: right;
    }
    .doc-meta .label {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #64748b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .doc-meta .value {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    /* ── Title Banner ── */
    .title-banner {
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .title-banner h1 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .title-banner p {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    /* ── Date + Reference ── */
    .date-ref {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #475569;
    }

    /* ── Address Block ── */
    .address-block {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .address-block p {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .address-block strong {
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ── Subject ── */
    .subject {
      background: #f0f4ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #1a1a2e;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }
    .subject p {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
    }
    .subject span {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #475569;
    }

    /* ── Body Text ── */
    .body-text {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      color: #334155;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    /* ── Loan Terms Table ── */
    .terms-card {
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .terms-header {
      background: #1e293b;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .terms-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .term-item {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      border-right: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }
    .term-item:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
    .term-item:last-child,
    .term-item:nth-last-child(2) {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .term-label {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #94a3b8;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .term-value {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    /* ── Conditions ── */
    .conditions {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .conditions h3 {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .conditions ol {
      padding-left: 16px;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 10px;
    }
    .conditions ol li {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    /* ── Signature ── */
    .signature-section {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .sig-block {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .sig-line {
      width: 160px;
      border-top: 1px solid #94a3b8;
      margin: 0 auto 4px;
    }
    .sig-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8.5px;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .footer strong {
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #1e40af;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div>
      <div class="bank-name">⬡ FORTRESS BANKING</div>
      <div class="bank-tagline">Trusted · Secure · Reliable · Since 1994</div>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-meta">
      <div class="label">Document Ref.</div>
      <div class="value">{{referenceNumber}}</div>
      <div class="label" style="margin-top:6px">Issued On</div>
      <div class="value">{{issueDate}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Title Banner -->
  <div class="title-banner">
    <h1>Official Sanction Letter</h1>
    <p>Loan Origination System &nbsp;|&nbsp; Confidential Document</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Date + Ref -->
  <div class="date-ref">
    <span>Date: <strong>{{issueDate}}</strong></span>
    <span>Application No.: <strong>{{applicationNumber}}</strong></span>
  </div>

  <!-- Address -->
  <div class="address-block">
    <p>To,</p>
    <p><strong>{{applicantName}}</strong></p>
    {{#if applicantAddress}}<p>{{applicantAddress}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if applicantCity}}<p>{{applicantCity}}{{#if applicantState}}, {{applicantState}}{{/if}}{{#if applicantPostalCode}} - {{applicantPostalCode}}{{/if}}</p>{{/if}}
    <p>Email: {{applicantEmail}}</p>
    <p>Phone: {{applicantPhone}}</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Subject -->
  <div class="subject">
    <p>Subject: Sanction of {{loanTypeDisplay}} — Application No. {{applicationNumber}}</p>
    <span>Dear {{applicantName}},</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
  <p class="body-text">
    We are pleased to inform you that your application for a <span class="highlight">{{loanTypeDisplay}}</span> has been
    reviewed and <strong>duly sanctioned</strong> by the Credit Committee of Fortress Banking Limited, subject to the
    terms and conditions detailed herein. This sanction is valid for a period of <strong>{{offerValidDays}} days</strong>
    from the date of this letter.
  </p>
  <p class="body-text">
    The sanction has been granted based on the information and documents provided by you. All details furnished by you
    are deemed correct and complete. Any misrepresentation may lead to cancellation of this sanction.
  </p>

  <!-- Loan Terms -->
  <div class="terms-card">
    <div class="terms-header">Sanctioned Loan Terms</div>
    <div class="terms-grid">
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Sanctioned Amount</div>
        <div class="term-value">₹{{loanAmount}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Rate of Interest</div>
        <div class="term-value">{{interestRate}}% p.a.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Loan Tenure</div>
        <div class="term-value">{{tenureMonths}} Months</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Monthly EMI</div>
        <div class="term-value">₹{{emiAmount}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Loan Type</div>
        <div class="term-value">{{loanTypeDisplay}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-item">
        <div class="term-label">Accepted On</div>
        <div class="term-value">{{acceptedDate}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Conditions -->
  <div class="conditions">
    <h3>Terms &amp; Conditions</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>The loan will be disbursed upon completion of all documentation, KYC formalities, and agreement signing.</li>
      <li>The EMI will be automatically debited from the registered bank account on the 5th of every month.</li>
      <li>Any prepayment of the loan will attract a prepayment charge as per the bank's prevailing policy.</li>
      <li>The sanctioned amount is non-transferable and must be used solely for the stated purpose.</li>
      <li>Fortress Banking reserves the right to recall the loan if any misrepresentation is discovered.</li>
      <li>This letter is subject to the execution of necessary loan agreements and mortgage deeds.</li>
      <li>Rate of interest is subject to change as per the bank's Base Rate revision from time to time.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <p class="body-text">
    We request you to visit your nearest Fortress Banking branch within <strong>{{offerValidDays}} days</strong> to
    complete the disbursement formalities. Please carry this letter along with the original KYC documents for
    verification.
  </p>

  <p class="body-text">
    We thank you for choosing Fortress Banking Limited and look forward to a long and mutually beneficial relationship.
  </p>

  <!-- Signature -->
  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="sig-block">
      <div class="sig-line"></div>
      <div class="sig-label">Applicant's Signature</div>
      <div class="sig-label" style="margin-top:2px"><strong>{{applicantName}}</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sig-block">
      <div class="sig-line"></div>
      <div class="sig-label">Authorized Signatory</div>
      <div class="sig-label" style="margin-top:2px"><strong>Fortress Banking Limited</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <strong>Fortress Banking Limited</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; CIN: L65191MH1994PLC081618 &nbsp;|&nbsp; RBI License: BANK/2024/FBL &nbsp;|&nbsp; IRDAI Reg: 123<br/>
    Registered Office: Fortress Tower, BKC, Mumbai - 400 051 &nbsp;|&nbsp; support@fortressbanking.com &nbsp;|&nbsp; 1800-123-4567<br/>
    <em>This is a computer-generated document. No signature is required on the digital copy.</em>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
